display_long_description:
Labyrinth is a multiplayer virtual reality experience focused on exploration, communication, and shared discovery.

Players enter a surreal world made of interconnected rooms where they can freely roam, talk with other players in real time, and explore environments filled with unexpected encounters. Each space offers something new to discover, encouraging curiosity and interaction.

As you move through the world, you may encounter strange creatures, wandering animals, hidden tokens, and unusual avatars. Some encounters are calm and mysterious, while others are more intense and interactive. Players can defend themselves, experiment with movement and shooting mechanics, and engage with the environment in dynamic ways.

The visual style blends dreamlike and nightmare-inspired elements, creating an atmosphere that feels both familiar and strange. The world is designed to feel alive and unpredictable, making each session different depending on who you meet and what you discover.

Labyrinth is designed as a social VR space where players can explore together, communicate freely, and experience emergent moments inside an ever-evolving virtual world.
